rath Lohitashwa]] and [[Arun Sagar]] in key supporting roles. While Late Actor [[Ambarish]] plays a cameo role, the popular late actor [[Vishnuvardhan (actor)|Vishnuvardhan]] appear on screen through a computer generated visual effect.<ref>[http://www.chitraloka.com/news/16773-you-can-see-sahasa-simha-in-rajasimha.html You can see Sahasa Simha in Rajasimha] Chitraloka (30 January 2018)</ref><ref>[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/kannada/movies/news/raja-simha-will-be-a-treat-for-fans-of-vishnuvardhan-films-anirudh/articleshow/62741264.cms Raja Simha will be a treat for fans of Vishnuvardhan films: Anirudh] Times of India (2 February 2018)</ref> The film is reported to be a sequel of Vishnuvardhan's hit ''[[Simhadriya Simha]]'' (2002).<ref>[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/kannada/movies/news/raja-simha-is-almost-a-sequel-to-simhadriya-simha/articleshow/62723902.cms Raja Simha is almost a sequel to Simhadriya Simha] Times of India (1 February 2018)</ref> The film's soundtrack is composed by [[Jassie Gift]] and the background score is by [[Sadhu Kokila]].\n\nThe film released across Karnataka on 2 February 2018.<ref>[http://www.chitraloka.com/news/16793-raja-simhana-rathayatre-from-today.html Raja Simhana Rathayatre From Today] Chitraloka (2 February 2018)</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Aniruddha Jatkar|Aniruddha]]\n* [[Nikita Thukral]]\n* [[Sanjjanaa]]\n* [[Bharathi Vishnuvardhan]]\n* [[Sharath Lohitashwa]]\n* [[Arun Sagar]]\n* [[Bullet Prakash]]\n* Vijay Chendur\n* [[Ambarish]] in a guest appearance\n* [[Vishnuvardhan (actor)|Vishnuvardhan]] through VFX.\n\n==Soundtrack==\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Rajasimha\n| type       = soundtrack\n| artist     = [[Jassie Gift]]\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| released   =\n| recorded   = 2017\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Film soundtrack|Feature film soundtrack]]\n| length     =\n| language   = [[Kannada language|Kannada]]\n| label      = Anand Audio\n| producer   = Jassie Gift\n| prev_title =\n| prev_year  =\n| next_title =\n| next_year  =\n}}\n\nThe film's soundtracks are composed by [[Jassie Gift]]. The music rights were acquired by Anand Audio.\n\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Tracklist\n| extra_column = Singer(s)\n| total_length = \n| title1 = Yentha Bhagya\n| lyrics1 = Nelamane Raghavendra\n| extra1 = [[L. N. Shastri]]\n| length1 = 04:40\n| title2 = Missamma Yamma\n| lyrics2 = [[Kaviraj (lyricist)|Kaviraj]]\n| extra2 = [[Jassie Gift]], [[Indu Nagaraj]]\n| length2 = 03:45\n| title3 = Khadak Kadhar\n| lyrics3 = Nelamane Raghavendra\n| extra3 = [[Tippu (singer)|Tippu]]\n| length3 = 04:20\n| title4 = Gulabu Jamunu\n| lyrics4 = Ghouse Peer\n| extra4 = [[Malathy Lakshman|Malathi]], C. D. Basappa\n| length4 =03:18\n| title5 = Bandha Devara Haage\n| lyrics5 = Nelamane Raghavendra\n| extra5 = Vikas Chintan, Suma Shastri\n| length5 =04:34\n| title6 = Baaro Nalla Baaro\n| lyrics6 = Nelamane Raghavendra\n| extra6 = [[Santhosh Venky]], [[Anuradha Bhat]]\n| length6 = 04:02\n|all_writing=|title9=|length9=|title10=|length10=|title11=|length11=|title12=|length12=|title13=|length13=|title14=|length14=|title15=|length15=|title16=|length16=|title17=|length17=|title18=|length18=|title19=|length19=|title20=|length20=}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|7976508}}\n* {{Twitter|rajasimha hashtag on twitter}}\n* [http://www.sandalwoodking.rocks/threads/raja-simha-movie-aniruddh-nikitha-thukral-ravi-jassie-gift-released.6128/page-4 Raja Simha Movie - Aniruddh, Nikitha Thukral - Ravi -Jassie Gift - Released]\n\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2010s Kannada-language films]]\n[[Category:2010s action films]]\n[[Category:Indian romance films]]\n[[Category:Indian action films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Mysore]]\n[[Category:2018 directorial debut films]]\n\n[[kn:\u0cb0\u0cbe\u0c9c\u0cb8\u0cbf\u0c82\u0cb9]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=March 2018}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name      