er Olympics \u2013 Men's 110 metres hurdles|Men's 110 m hurdles]]\n| ?\n| x\n|colspan=4| Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left| [[Kanematsu Yamada]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's marathon|Men's Marathon]]\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| 2:35.29\n| 4\n|-\n|align=left| [[Seiichiro Tsuda]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's marathon|Men's Marathon]]\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| 2:36.20\n| 6\n|-\n|rowspan=3 align=left| [[Mikio Oda]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's long jump|Men's Long Jump]]\n| 7.11\n| 11 \n| colspan=6| Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's triple jump|Men's Triple Jump]]\n| 15.21 \n| 1\n| x\n| x\n|15.21\n|{{gold01}}\n|-\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's high jump|Men's High Jump]]\n|1.83 \n|1\n| x\n| x\n|1.88 \n|7\n|-\n|rowspan=2 align=left| [[Ch\u016bhei Nambu]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's long jump|Men's Long Jump]]\n| 7.25\n| 9 \n| colspan=6| Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's triple jump|Men's Triple Jump]]\n| 15.01 \n| 2\n| x\n| x\n|15.01\n| 4\n|-\n|align=left| [[Kazuo Kimura]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's high jump|Men's High Jump]]\n|1.83 \n|1\n| x\n| x\n|1.88 \n|6\n|-\n|rowspan=2 align=left| [[Yonetaro Nakazawa]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's pole vault|Men's Pole Vault]]\n|3.66 \n|1\n| x\n| x\n|3.90 \n|6\n|-\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's decathlon|Men's decathlon]]\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| 4795 \n| 22\n|-\n|rowspan=2 align=left| [[Yoshio Okita]]\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's discus throw|Men's Discus Throw]]\n| x\n| x\n|36.38\n|30\n| colspan=6| Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left| [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's hammer throw|Men'